# Documentation

Use these docs in this order:

## Consumer Track
- Start with [Platform Docs](platform/README.md).
- Follow [First 30 Minutes](platform/consumer/first_30_minutes.md).
- Use [Platform Quickstart](platform/consumer/quickstart.md) for the default bootstrap flow.
- Review [Platform Troubleshooting](platform/consumer/troubleshooting.md) when operating the repo.

## Blueprint Reference Track
- Use [Blueprint Docs](blueprint/README.md) only when you need inherited contract, ownership, or bootstrap details.
- Start with [Blueprint Execution Model](blueprint/architecture/execution_model.md) and [Ownership Matrix](blueprint/governance/ownership_matrix.md).

